      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's good to hear. I noticed a couple of the subcontractor logs from last week mentioned some issues with the concrete delivery and the foundation crew being behind. Can you clarify if those are just minor hiccups or if they're actually going to impact the Q4 deadline?",
